{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "丁典与狄云遭万震山二弟子周圻、马大鸣、耿天霸三人围攻，丁典中毒后仍奋力搏杀，将连城诀口诀逐字传给狄云后力竭身亡。狄云抱丁典尸身逃入菜园柴房，意外遇见师妹戚芳及其女空心菜，得知戚芳已嫁万圭。万圭追至柴房与狄云搏斗，用计刺伤狄云后昏厥。狄云昏迷中被人救上小舟漂流江中，醒后发现伤口已被包扎，身旁留有碎银和首饰，救命恩人身份成谜。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "兄弟，我说的那四个数目字，你记住了么？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "兄弟，你记住了没有？",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "第一字是⋯⋯",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "赞许",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_ming",
      "speaker_name": "马大鸣",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "姓丁的，你总算也是条汉子，怎么到了这地步，还在婆婆妈妈的啰唆不休？快跟咱兄弟们乖乖回去，大家免伤和气。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_qi",
      "speaker_name": "周圻",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "狄大哥，多年不见，你好啊？牢狱中住得挺舒服罢？",
      "tone": "讥讽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_zhou_qi",
      "text": "原来是周⋯⋯周⋯⋯周二哥！",
      "tone": "强压愤怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "赞许",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "这位周二爷，想必是万老爷子门下的高弟。很好，很好，你几时到了凌知府手下当差？狄兄弟，我给你引见引见。这位是'万胜刀'门中的马大鸣马爷。那位是山西太行门外家好手，'双刀'耿天霸耿爷。据说他一对铁掌锋利如刀，因此外号'双刀'，其实他是从来不使兵刃的。",
      "tone": "从容不迫",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "这两位的武功怎样？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "第三流中的好手。要想攀到第二流，却终生无望。",
      "tone": "轻蔑",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "不是那一块材料，资质既差，又没名师传授。",
      "tone": "轻描淡写",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "耿天霸",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "直娘贼，死到临头，还在乱嚼舌根。吃我一刀！",
      "tone": "暴怒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "耿天霸",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "怎么样？我是第三流，你是第几流？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_ming",
      "speaker_name": "马大鸣",
      "listener": "char_zhou_qi",
      "text": "周兄弟，并肩子上！",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_qi",
      "speaker_name": "周圻",
      "listener": "char_ma_da_ming",
      "text": "是啊！",
      "tone": "附和",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "狄兄弟，退下。",
      "tone": "喝令",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "狄兄弟，你听我的话。你躲在我身后，不必去理会敌人，只管记我的口诀。这事非同小可，咱们说什么也得办成功了。你丁大哥落到今日这步田地，便是为此。",
      "tone": "郑重",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "第五个字是'十八'⋯⋯",
      "tone": "低声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "第六个字是'七'。",
      "tone": "低声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_geng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "耿天霸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，别着了他道儿！",
      "tone": "大喝",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "狄兄弟，记住第七字，那是⋯⋯",
      "tone": "急促",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_zhou_qi",
      "text": "狄兄弟，快走，快走！",
      "tone": "大叫",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "狄兄弟，快走，你别顾我，我⋯⋯我总是不活的了！",
      "tone": "大叫",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "要死，大家死在一起！",
      "tone": "坚决",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "好兄弟，你义气深重⋯⋯不枉我⋯⋯交了你这朋友⋯⋯那剑诀⋯⋯可惜说不全了⋯⋯我⋯⋯我很快活⋯⋯春水碧波⋯⋯那盆绿色的菊花⋯⋯嗯！她放在窗口，你瞧多美啊⋯⋯菊花⋯⋯",
      "tone": "临终遗言",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_zhou_qi",
      "text": "放开丁大哥！",
      "tone": "大叫",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_zhou_qi",
      "text": "丁大哥，丁大哥！",
      "tone": "惊恐",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我⋯⋯我⋯⋯和你同归于尽。",
      "tone": "悲愤",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "丁大哥，丁大哥。你⋯⋯你⋯⋯怎么样？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "丁大哥，我⋯⋯我说什么也要救你出去。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dian",
      "speaker_name": "丁典",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "可惜⋯⋯可惜那剑诀，从此⋯⋯从此失传了，合葬⋯⋯霜华⋯⋯",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "你放心！我记得的⋯⋯定要将你和凌小姐合葬，完了你二人心愿。",
      "tone": "大声承诺",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_guai_renzhu",
      "speaker_name": "搜索队",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马大爷、耿大爷、周二爷，见到了逃犯没有？",
      "tone": "呼喊",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_guai_renzhu",
      "speaker_name": "搜索队",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "进去瞧瞧！",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_guai_renzhu",
      "speaker_name": "搜索队",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不会躲在这地方的。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_guai_renzhu",
      "speaker_name": "搜索队",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎知道？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "speaker_name": "空心菜",
      "listener": "char_qi_fang",
      "text": "妈，妈，我在这儿！",
      "tone": "清脆",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "text": "空心菜，你躲到那儿啦？妈到处找你不着。",
      "tone": "柔和",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "speaker_name": "空心菜",
      "listener": "char_qi_fang",
      "text": "空心菜在花园！空心菜看蚂蚁！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "text": "空心菜自己会玩，真乖！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "text": "空心菜别在这里玩，跟妈妈回房去。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "speaker_name": "空心菜",
      "listener": "char_qi_fang",
      "text": "这里好玩，空心菜要看蚂蚁。",
      "tone": "执拗",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "text": "不，今天外面有坏人，要捉小孩子。空心菜还是回房里去罢。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "speaker_name": "空心菜",
      "listener": "char_qi_fang",
      "text": "什么坏人？捉小孩子做什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "text": "监牢里逃走了两个很凶很凶的坏人。爸爸去捉坏人去啦。坏人到了这里，就捉空心菜去。空心菜听妈妈的话，回房去玩。妈给你做个布娃娃，好不好？",
      "tone": "哄劝",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "speaker_name": "空心菜",
      "listener": "char_qi_fang",
      "text": "不要布娃娃。空心菜帮爸爸捉坏人。",
      "tone": "倔强",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "text": "快放下孩子！",
      "tone": "厉喝",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "放下我孩子！",
      "tone": "怒喝",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "是⋯⋯是你么？",
      "tone": "惊愕",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "我⋯⋯我不知道是你。这许多年来⋯⋯",
      "tone": "哽咽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_gui",
      "speaker_name": "万圭",
      "listener": "char_qi_fang",
      "text": "芳妹，芳妹！你在那里？",
      "tone": "呼唤",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "text": "空心菜，这伯伯不是坏人，你别跟爹爹说。知道么？",
      "tone": "低声叮嘱",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_gui",
      "speaker_name": "万圭",
      "listener": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "text": "空心菜，别哭。爹爹在这儿！",
      "tone": "安抚",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_gui",
      "speaker_name": "万圭",
      "listener": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "text": "空心菜为什么哭？",
      "tone": "笑问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_wan_gui",
      "text": "我和空心菜在后门口玩，两骑马奔过，马上的人拿了兵刃，长相挺凶的。空心菜说是坏人，要捉了她去，吓得大哭。",
      "tone": "笑答",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_gui",
      "speaker_name": "万圭",
      "listener": "char_kong_xin_cai",
      "text": "那是府衙门里追拿逃犯。来，爹爹抱空心菜。爹爹打死坏人。空心菜不怕坏人。爹爹把坏人一个个都打死了。",
      "tone": "哄逗",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_gui",
      "speaker_name": "万圭",
      "listener": "char_qi_fang",
      "text": "好像柴房里有人。",
      "tone": "警觉",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "戚芳",
      "listener": "char_wan_gui",
      "text": "是吗？刚才我见老王进去搬柴。圭哥，我给你炖了燕窝，快去吃了罢。空心菜老是哭个不休，得让她好好睡一觉。",
      "tone": "笑答掩饰",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_gui",
      "speaker_name": "万圭",
      "listener": "char_qi_fang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "应声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_gui",
      "speaker_name": "万圭",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "好啊，在柴房里相会，她连自己的兵刃也给了你，想谋杀亲夫么？只怕没这么容易！",
      "tone": "冷嘲",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_gui",
      "speaker_name": "万圭",
      "listener": "char_qi_fang",
      "text": "戚芳，你来看！",
      "tone": "大叫使诈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_gui",
      "speaker_name": "万圭",
      "listener": "char_di_yun",
      "text": "装死吗？",
      "tone": "骂道",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": "char_ding_dian",
      "text": "丁大哥！",
      "tone": "大叫",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "丁大哥，你在这里！",
      "tone": "惊喜",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_yun",
      "speaker_name": "狄云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "丁大哥，丁大哥！",
      "tone": "焦急大叫",
      "chapter": 4
    }
  ],
